Frequently Asked Questions ( FAQ )

I made the payment but didn’t receive any email

Please write to : hi@growthschool.io, our awesome support team will get back to you in 24 hours.
When does the workshop start?

The workshop is on the 8th November, 2020 from 2PM IST to 6PM IST
What are the pre-requisites?

Common sense is the only pre-requisite for the workshop.
Anyone with any or no experience in SEO can attend the workshop.

 
 
 
Will this be live or pre-recorded?

This is a completely live session. The live session link will be sent to your registered Email ID 1 hour before the workshop starts. We don't provide recordings of the session.

 
 
 
Would there be any certificate on completion?

Yes! You will receive a certificate on completion of the workshop. You must attend the full workshop to get the certificate.

 
 
 
When can I receive the bonuses?

You will receive additional bonuses at the end of the workshop

 
 
 
Will you provide the recording of the workshop?

This is strictly an online workshop and we dont provide any recordings.

 
 
 
Can I make a lot of money after the workshop?

This is not a get rich quick scheme. You will learn the SEO techniques that work and it is totally on you how much you implement and make out of it.
